  "body": "There are a few funcs to check if we're on NTFS. For example in LCOW:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/containerd/containerd/blob/574bde08ba1a698d96fd4a294443ea90fd7bd213/snapshots/lcow/lcow.go#L410\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/containerd/containerd/blob/574bde08ba1a698d96fd4a294443ea90fd7bd213/snapshots/lcow/lcow.go#L433\r\n\r\nAnd then in the Windows snapshotter:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/containerd/containerd/blob/574bde08ba1a698d96fd4a294443ea90fd7bd213/snapshots/windows/windows.go#L344\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/containerd/containerd/blob/574bde08ba1a698d96fd4a294443ea90fd7bd213/snapshots/windows/windows.go#L367\r\n\r\nIt would be nice to have these public and outside of the specific snapshotter implementations so they can be shared and re-used.\r\n\r\n/cc @jterry75 ",
